  "events": [],
  "moments": [
    {
      "id": "mo_001",
      "text": "I'd kill for someone to just yell 'YES THIS LOOKS FINE' at me.",
      "tone": "frustrated",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_002",
      "text": "It's so finicky — like I'm overthinking it, but I can't shake the feeling it's holding the whole thing back.",
      "tone": "frustrated",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_003",
      "text": "It's like it's resisting me.",
      "tone": "frustrated",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_004",
      "text": "I'm waiting for a spark that's not coming. Tension hai all around.",
      "tone": "anxious",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_005",
      "text": "I think I need to stop trying so hard and start playing.",
      "tone": "hopeful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_006",
      "text": "But honestly, I'm scared to even try. What if it makes it worse?",
      "tone": "scared",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_007",
      "text": "Tea is my soul, honestly.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_008",
      "text": "I miss live music these days, especially with folks who get the vibe.",
      "tone": "lonely",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_009",
      "text": "Their lyrics are so raw, it's like they're singing my thoughts.",
      "tone": "grateful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_010",
      "text": "It's like they're singing straight into the quiet corners of my brain.",
      "tone": "grateful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_011",
      "text": "Music is my glue.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_012",
      "text": "Old songs are like comfort food. When life feels chaotic, I need the familiar.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "mentions": 1
    }
  ],
